{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":24353,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"可以看看笛卡尔的第一哲学沉思集？","timestamp":1592898726,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24373,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"中国哲学简史 苏菲的世界","timestamp":1592898879,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24395,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"西方哲学：推荐看《苏菲的世界》，这是一本小说，其实是披着故事书外衣的西方哲学史。罗素写的《西方哲学史》也可以看，不过要难一些。了解西方哲学史之后就可以看一些名家的著作。中国哲学：感觉中国哲学没有西方哲学有体系，了解不多，好像也有《中国哲学史》。我看过老子的《道德经》，感觉也还挺有意思。","timestamp":1592899003,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24435,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"柏拉国的理想图（手动狗头）","timestamp":1592899260,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24533,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"艾思奇《大众哲学》","timestamp":1592900093,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24538,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"赞同Bob 看了这两本之后可以挑感兴趣的方面去接着看了","timestamp":1592900127,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24649,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 那个好像有点过于口语化，，，感觉不太哲学","timestamp":1592900903,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":24741,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"《苏菲的世界》很不错，然后可以接着看《大问题》或者《哲学的邀请》。再往后就根据自己的兴趣选取对应的书本了。","timestamp":1592901531,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25039,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"远离存在主义","timestamp":1592904647,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":25304,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 如果想哲学，黑格尔《逻辑学》、谢林《世界时代》是思辨哲学顶峰","timestamp":1592907502,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":26051,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":4079,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Hans: 为啥","timestamp":1592913891,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":15,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":4079,"reply":11,"tag":null,"text":"（模仿前面）\n哲学如何入门？看哪些书？\n（来自对哲学没有认知的大一工科生）","timestamp":1592898661,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782585,"url":"","vote":{}}}